The '''fero xyn''' was a creature native to the [[Yuuzhan Vong galaxy]]. Like all other life forms related to the [[Yuuzhan Vong]], the fero xyn had no connection with [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]. Yuuzhan Vong [[Shaper caste|Shapers]] combined this creature's genetic material with those of the [[vornskr]] to create the [[voxyn]].

The fero xyn spat a [[Poison/Legends|poison]] similar to the voxyn.<ref name="Mission to Myrkr web enhancement">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20020207myrkr|text=Mission to Myrkr|int=Mission to Myrkr (web enhancement)}}</ref>

